snippet.title: CAONA - Game Teaser | Unreal Engine 5
snippet.description:
CAONA is an Action Adventure Game currently in early development.

Discover Caona, an upcoming action-adventure game set in a rich and immersive world inspired by South American mythology. Fight powerful deities and mystical creatures to keep the world safe.



This is an Indie Game.

---
https://risingnine.com
https://twitter.com/RisingNine

Project Collaborators:
Music: Ricky Leroy Brown
Mocap Actress: Luna Semadeni
Sound FX: https://stephencshapiro.com
